              <span>Clinical studies were conducted on adults with a BMI of 26 or higher. Results may vary outside this range.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-out">
            <div>
              <div class="out-lab" id="weaOutLab">Your 3-Month Potential</div>
